\section{System Architecture: The Self-Referential Loop}
\label{sec:architecture}

\subsection{High-Level Overview: A Closed Dialectical Circuit}
The X-DPAS architecture implements Axiom ASR via a \textbf{closed loop} (Figure \ref{fig:xdpas_architecture}), not a linear pipeline:
\begin{enumerate}
    \item \textbf{The Analytical Function ($\Phi$):} Applies dialectical logic to external system data.
    \item \textbf{The Meta-Analytical Function ($\Gamma$):} Applies the same logic to the outputs of $\Phi$.
\end{enumerate}

This creates a \textbf{genetic development cycle} for the system's own analytical rules.

