\subsection{The Analytical Function ($\Phi$): Core Analysis Engine}
The $\Phi$ function is instantiated in the main analyzer class \cite{xenopoulou2024xdpas}. Its primary method orchestrates data preparation, risk metric calculation, paradox detection, XEPTQLRI computation, and report synthesis.

