\textbf{Data \& Benchmarks:} Greek daily data (EODY) \cite{eody2023data} vs. ARIMA \cite{box1970time} \& LSTM \cite{hochreiter1997long}.\\
\textbf{Results:} X-DPAS achieved \textbf{74.2\% accuracy} with \textbf{84-day lead time} (Table \ref{tab:predictive_performance}).

